#12803
The darkening forest~
Shadows crawl across the forest floor, while strange sounds call out
from behind the trees.  Here the path splits offering three choices...
South the forest seems to thin out and the sun shines unopposed.
North the shadows continue to close in on the path.
East another less worn path leads, and you can hear the trickle of water.
