#12805
Upstream~
As you wade upstream through the brook, you hear the delighted laugh 
of water pixies playing about you.  Silver fish dart here and there
curiously examining you and then speeding away at your first move.
The brook continues to climb the hill side to the north, and 
tumbles gleefully down the hill to the south.
