The Spring~
As you reach the spring that feeds this happy little brook you notice  
gleaming eyes watch you from above.  The ground around the spring is
torn up as if some malicious creature had just stomped through here.
Sadly the dense foliage of the forest prevents you from continuing 
in any direction except south...
