The growing stream~
Here the current of the stream tugs at your feet as you walk.
The trees of the forest rise to either side of you and the sounds
of animals are nearly drowned out by the rushing water.  To the
north the stream narrows into a brook, while south the current picks
up as other brooks feed it.
