#12809
The Rapids~
The river is angry here, running with abandon to the south.  Sharp 
rocks jutt out of the water like teeth, churning the water, changing 
it to the white foam of rapids.  You see a piece of driftwood fly
by you and smash itself to splinters on the rocks.  You are faced
with a choice, go north to away from the rapids, or south into
the angry river's mouth
